==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Alamode
<hw>Al"a*mode`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A thin, black silk for hoods,
scarfs, etc.; -- often called simply <xex>mode</xex>.</def>
<rj><au>Buchanan.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

